{"tid":1374476,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教大家如何分辨軍師／風向Post","createTime":"2019-07-27T18:58:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T00:21:47.000Z","uid":56157,"like":164,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"661548cc5c20843d558829bea7f72d1a36c19fb4","tid":1374476,"uid":56157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T18:58:33.000Z","msg":"講真，呢個星期太多風向Post。佢地自稱係冷氣軍師<br />\n但實際上做既野其實係帶風向。<br />\n咁咩先係所謂真正既軍師Post？舉個例：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">圍村地圖APP<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/doKvnT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/doKvnT</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">［臨急抱佛腳系列］727元朗，200蚊內買齊野餐基本裝備<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dqvPzT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dqvPzT</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">【文化輸出】法國人疑似學香港人用水淋熄催淚彈<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/djKugT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/djKugT</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢啲裝備，地圖，應對警察攻擊既Post先係真正既軍師Post，無論任何人睇左都會有幫助，也唔會影響其他人如何行動</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n乜野唔係軍師Post而係風向Post？舉另一個例：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">727奇招： 智取元朗！道德抗暴！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dqADrT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dqADrT</a></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">叫人智取叫人提早撤退但沒有給出任何行動方案同建議，明顯只係影響大家對於行動既價值觀，第一句仲用正皮幫自己辯護同埋仲係Ｐ牌</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">[727元朗] 求下大家聽日唔好主動出手<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dqDfvT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dqDfvT</a></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">自High自己嬴緊，挾民意以令群眾</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n搞清楚其實咁多場運動一直講緊無大台，「Be Water」。<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">「Be Water」既真正意思係隨機應變，每個人應該用自己獨立思考方式黎決定點樣行動，而唔係信左某些意見／正皮Post。</span></strong>係現場，你決定留或退係你自己個人決定，但你唔應該影響其他人點樣行動。<br />\n<br />\n正如衝立法會班示威者有以下想法：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">Daisy和Nick在衝擊後一方面不斷轉換居所，到不同朋友家暫住，避免警方追捕。另一方面聯絡律師，為被捕做好準備。他們很驚慌，擔心會被捕，但5年來他們嘗試各種方法，最後結論是只有訴諸暴力才有效。Daisy、Nick和他們的同伴一樣，並非一開始便認為和平示威無用，但歷時79天的佔中運動沒有帶來一點改變，對他們是很大打擊。Nick說：「事件顯示若你採取和平方式、只在街頭靜坐，政府會毫不關心。在他們眼中，你們只是一群坐在街上的人。」他又說：「我們已沒有甚麼可輸，這就是我們開始反抗的原因。」</span></strong></span><br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190705/59789443\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190705%2F59789443&d=ajJRCbjZ3CJF8zdY8%2Fu%2F1%2F%2BqeKGcMvuhkm4gAZs5aLs%3D&h=a6083e15\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190705%2F59789443&h=b4480ff4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190705/59789443</a><br />\n<br />\n大量風向Post同帶風向既人仲不停咁質問所謂前線或者勇武派留守又點，乜野戰略地點，有冇成效。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">點樣行動係由「行動」嗰班人自己決定，唔需要你班風向撚係度發聲，你覺得無成效，你可以先走，但唔好帶風向影響其他人。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>記住無大台，Be Water，獨立思考，先係唯一既真正共識。其他乜野共識一切都只係帶風向。</strong></span>"},{"pid":"629a9f3c4bd1b24c8bae95073668f104dc8d6ede","tid":1374476,"uid":8482,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T19:00:08.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽日見<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cGdMduz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcGdMduz.png&h=71412d90&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"84209619580da164961692f56da7368467523aa7","tid":1374476,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T19:01:04.000Z","msg":"「長文」抗爭除Be Water外，Assassin's Creed嘅信條你都一定要識！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1374405\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1374405</a>"},{"pid":"d971508a83ecffb758ad64a300eed8b8fac1cb4f","tid":1374476,"uid":771,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T19:03:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2fea95d0035122824ddd06ce5d4dbc8f87b1ad82","tid":1374476,"uid":160176,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T19:04:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a46034de4ef28881d0d3680b176c4dbcaee25b22","tid":1374476,"uid":216907,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T19:05:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>大力推！</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97cdca7c64cc1e7f3b8f06761e8de73abd57e4f6","tid":1374476,"uid":236538,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T19:06:00.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫幫手唔該<br />\n<br />\n一句講哂 現場自主決定散唔散 咪睇連登任何撤既po!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1374335\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1374335</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b2515291e8799efa3980181c3ff1f35e40201837","tid":1374476,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T19:10:42.000Z","msg":"PISH"},{"pid":"b1adf04f47e9e085021edf8dd3686ca9c01da767","tid":1374476,"uid":130140,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T19:10:45.000Z","msg":"唔肯定係風向定軍師嘅話，請唔好有任何動作（正負評、回po）<br />\n<br />\n諗清楚再決定幫唔幫推"},{"pid":"56aac863398420c73fc73c26943a1e05e88c8cc9","tid":1374476,"uid":56157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T20:59:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"757eb7072932f9a21ebe08ccf25054dfc439057a","tid":1374476,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T21:13:51.000Z","msg":"你呢個 post 要上熱門 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/nor